  <name>Terminal</name>
  <summary>A lightweight multiplatform terminal emulator</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
        Hawaii Terminal is a lightweight and easy to use multiplatform
        terminal emulator for accessing a UNIX shell environment which
        can be used to run programs available on your system.
    <p>
        Its main features are:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Profiles and color schemes</li>
      <li>Multiple tabs</li>
      <li>Horizontal and vertical split</li>
      <li>Text search</li>
      <li>Easy user interface</li>
      <li>Full screen mode</li>
      <li>Integration with system clipboard</li>
      <li>Dynamic line wrapping</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
